					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I just looked through the comments to make sure, and I think I'm correct&#8230;</p> <p>Am I the only person who finds this sad? After I got over the &quot;whaaaaat&quot; factor and put it all together, my next thought was sadness. &quot;I have to support my mother&quot;, and then he gets cursed, put in a tree, and his one possession gets taken away from him. I can't imagine he can walk normally, seeing as he has very little friction. It just&#8230; maybe I'm just in a mood, but one of my first thoughts was &quot;god damn this is sad.&quot;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
