					<![CDATA[
						 <p>What I particularly enjoy about this SCP is how completely pathetic SCP-1728 is, like a wrestler receiving an iron-man suit and, instead of going on a super villain rampage, uses it to win a wrestling competition, simply because that's the only thing they can think to do with it and nothing else.</p> 
