					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-643075#post-1751146</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-643075/scp-1728#post-1751146</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2013 17:43:24 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>PetraCore</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1356996</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I have to admit, if there wasn't any story at all I probably wouldn't like it. But there's enough hints of a perfectly fairytale like story here that I adore it. Sure, it seems random at first glance, but it makes perfect sense, <em>in a fairytale frame</em>, for this kid to be headless and leaking butter constantly, given his crime. The clinical tone just heightens the weirdness, which to me reflects on how weird every fairytale is, really, when you think about it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
